      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride with plenty of character? This car is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! It shows some honest wear and tear, but it has been a dependable companion and still has plenty of life left to give. It's the perfect choice for someone looking for a solid, budget-friendly vehicle that gets the job done with a smile!",
