    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and there are no chips, scratches, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather still smelling new and all electronic features and climate controls functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and zero wear on the engine or suspension. A buyer can expect a vehicle that is indistinguishable from a brand-new model in every respect.",
      "price": 49800.0,
